articles.title: SpaceX Gets FAA Clearance to Resume Falcon 9 Launches - Techopedia
articles.description: SpaceX has received Federal Aviation Administration (FAA) clearance to resume Falcon 9 rocket launches while the agency investigates a mid-flight failure from earlier this month.
